EN: This truck can carry up to five tons.

ZH: 路上有一辆货车失控了。
EN: A truck lost control on the road.

ZH: 那辆货车在工地上卸货。
EN: The truck is unloading at the construction site.

ZH: 他开着货车送货到客户家中。
EN: He drives a truck to deliver goods to customers.

ZH: 我们需要一辆大型货车来搬运设备。
EN: We need a large truck to transport the equipment.

ZH: 请小心驾驶货车，避免交通事故。
EN: Please drive the truck carefully to avoid traffic accidents.

ZH: 这辆货车的引擎出了故障。
EN: The engine of this truck broke down.

ZH: 老板买了一辆新的货车扩大生意。
EN: The boss bought a new truck to expand the business.

ZH: 这辆货车的轮胎需要更换。
EN: The tires of this truck need to be replaced.

ZH: 那辆货车载着蔬菜去市场。
EN: The truck is carrying vegetables to the market.

ZH: 家里的货车正在维修中。
EN: The truck at home is under repair.

ZH: 经过数小时的驾驶，货车到达目的地。
EN: After hours of driving, the truck arrived at the destination.

ZH: 他们用货车搬运了一大批书籍到学校。
EN: They used a truck to transport a large batch of books to the school.

ZH: 这辆货车的装卸速度很快。
EN: The loading and unloading speed of this truck is very fast.

ZH: 那辆货车在夜间连续行驶了数百公里。
EN: The truck drove hundreds of kilometers continuously at night.

ZH: 骑自行车的小孩差点被货车撞到。
EN: The child riding a bike was almost hit by a truck.

ZH: 这辆货车的尾灯坏了，需要维修。
EN: The tail light of this truck is broken and needs to be repaired.
